    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dangerous Roads</i> is a fantasy tower defense adventure where a small band of heroes stands between the kingdom and total destruction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead of static defenses, you command a party of three adventurers defending the trade roads from waves of invading monsters such as zombies, orcs, trolls, bats, dragons, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/8f23258fe8a4cdb1b4fe987866fc8f9e.poster.avif?t=1772079160\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/8f23258fe8a4cdb1b4fe987866fc8f9e.webm?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/8f23258fe8a4cdb1b4fe987866fc8f9e.mp4?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your party wisely:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Knight</strong> – your frontline defender with high health and durability</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/1f67fbb18286e6f643ce71bff08ccea6.poster.avif?t=1772079160\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/1f67fbb18286e6f643ce71bff08ccea6.webm?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/1f67fbb18286e6f643ce71bff08ccea6.mp4?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Wizard</strong> – devastating firepower but fragile</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/0105ac7291959d8f9eb8947cac7fc51e.poster.avif?t=1772079160\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/0105ac7291959d8f9eb8947cac7fc51e.webm?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/0105ac7291959d8f9eb8947cac7fc51e.mp4?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Druid</strong> – supports allies and can still fight when needed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/5a771abf2360e7385551e6767c631c58.poster.avif?t=1772079160\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/5a771abf2360e7385551e6767c631c58.webm?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/5a771abf2360e7385551e6767c631c58.mp4?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Across 8 increasingly difficult levels, enemies grow stronger and attack from multiple paths, forcing you to adapt your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gold you save after each battle carries into the next mission. Managing your resources is the key to survival. Spend too early and you will not last. Save too much and you may not survive the present wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/20120f83e9c6c6635a29545dd8eb5c10.poster.avif?t=1772079160\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/20120f83e9c6c6635a29545dd8eb5c10.webm?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/20120f83e9c6c6635a29545dd8eb5c10.mp4?t=1772079160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your defenses, balance your party, and hold the road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because if the roads fall, the kingdom falls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Thank you for choosing to play <i>Dangerous Roads</i>. We truly appreciate your support and hope you enjoy your time defending the realm.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras/79c32a3a44d0ee74919af516c5bbf87c.avif?t=1772079160\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196220/extras_big/79c32a3a44d0ee74919af516c5bbf87c.webp?t=1772079160 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p>",
